    • Constructor Detail

      • RadarTrip

        public RadarTrip(java.lang.String _id,
                 java.lang.String externalId,
                 org.json.JSONObject metadata,
                 java.lang.String destinationGeofenceTag,
                 java.lang.String destinationGeofenceExternalId,
                 RadarCoordinate destinationLocation,
                 Radar.RadarRouteMode mode,
                 java.lang.Double etaDistance,
                 java.lang.Double etaDuration,
                 RadarTrip.RadarTripStatus status)

        Represents a trip.

        Parameters:
        _id - The Radar ID of the trip.
        externalId - The external ID of the trip.
        metadata - The optional set of custom key-value pairs for the trip.
        destinationGeofenceTag - For trips with a destination, the tag of the destination geofence.
        destinationGeofenceExternalId - For trips with a destination, the external ID of the destination geofence.
        destinationLocation - For trips with a destination, the location of the destination geofence.
        mode - The travel mode for the trip.
        etaDistance - For trips with a destination, the distance to the destination geofence in meters based on the travel mode for the trip.
        etaDuration - For trips with a destination, the ETA to the destination geofence in minutes based on the travel mode for the trip.
        status - The status of the trip.
